::Atma and Psuedo finally come across the neutral base.  When they arrive, 
they see Technosis with a couple other bots. Psuedo calls out::
Psuedo: Technosis!! Were back! Its me Psuedo!
Atma: How've you been doing Technosis?!
~~~~~
::Time Warp couldnt beleive his eyes::
Time Warp: Well... i guess things on this planet have changed in our absence. 
Do you think Infectra's with the Maximals?
